Aim: WAP in java to enter 1 to 20 numbers using 1D array and print even numbers only.
Solution:
public class EvenNos {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int[] arr = new int[20];
        for (int i = 0; i < 20; i++) {
            arr[i] = i + 1;
        }
        for (int i = 0; i < 20; i++) {
            if (arr[i] % 2 == 0) {
                System.out.println(arr[i]);
            }
        }
    }
}
